Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.44,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Hey what is it？Watch your step now！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.20,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}并不需要常识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:18.91,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Are you serious！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.91,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}No No No don't worry  One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.08,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}沉默的心脏 再次传来跳动的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:28.37,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使视野很混乱 但是不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:35.51,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}你还相信着 我不会背叛你
